name: This level
description:
Acrylic and paper collage, signed. This composition show romance and different layers and leves of interpretation. The couple, the relationship, the third entity created. I signed this piece on 2021 to call it finished, but was created during different years, adjusting and changing details, as you can see from the survived surface with little scratches that bring some real life story to the image. 
more of my art on instagram @hansessions
(6130×6253) High Quality
